Key j A 4 Next (CurrentPage, !Iconic) EWMHActivateWindowFunc
Key k A 4 Prev (CurrentPage, !Iconic) EWMHActivateWindowFunc

Key Backslash A 4 Exec exec $[fvwm_editor]
Key Return A 4 Exec exec $[fvwm_terminal]
Key f A 4 Exec exec $[fvwm_filemanager]

Key i A C4 Prev (CurrentPage, Iconic) EWMHActivateWindowFunc

Key l A 4 RaiseLower

DestroyFunc FuncFvwmRestore
AddToFunc   FuncFvwmRestore
+ I ThisWindow (!Iconic !Shaded Maximized) Maximize    false
+ I ThisWindow (!Iconic  Shaded          ) WindowShade false
+ I ThisWindow ( Iconic                  ) Iconify     false


Key F5 WTSF1234567890 4 Maximize 100 100
