Key F2 A S4 FvwmRearrange -tile -h 0 0 100 100 -animate

# Move mouse cursor out of the way to lower right corner
Key o A 4 CursorMove 100 100

Mouse 3 W C None
Mouse 2 W C None
Mouse 2 T N Lower

