+ I Move
+ D EWMHActivateWindowFunc
+ H EWMHActivateWindowFunc

# middle click and drag on icons to move them
Mouse 2 I N DragIcon
Mouse 3 I N DragOrDeIconify

DestroyFunc DragIcon
AddToFunc DragIcon
+ I Move

