# =================================================================
# FvwmPiazza
# =================================================================
# All (FvwmPiazza) Close
# DestroyModuleConfig FvwmPiazza: *
# #Struts: left right top bottom
# *FvwmPiazza: Struts 0 0 0 72
# *FvwmPiazza: Exclude (Gweled|gnome-mastermind|eog|feh|gcolor2|mplayer|xclock)
# #*FvwmPiazza: Layout0 Columns 2,37:52
# *FvwmPiazza: Layout0 None
# *FvwmPiazza: Layout1 None
# *FvwmPiazza: Layout2 None
# *FvwmPiazza: Layout3 None
# *FvwmPiazza: Layout4 None
# *FvwmPiazza: Layout5 None
# *FvwmPiazza: Layout6 None
# *FvwmPiazza: Layout7 None
# *FvwmPiazza: Layout8 None
# *FvwmPiazza: Layout9 None

#Module FvwmPiazza

# Hotkeys
# Key n               A       4       SendToModule FvwmPiazza "None"
# Key f               A       4S      SendToModule FvwmPiazza Full
# Key t               A       4       SendToModule FvwmPiazza Tall 3
# Key t               A       4S      SendToModule FvwmPiazza Tall 3,Right
# Key c               A       CM4     SendToModule FvwmPiazza Columns 2
# Key c               A       4S      SendToModule FvwmPiazza Columns 3,18:64:18
# Key p               A       4       SendToModule FvwmPiazza Rows 2
# Key p               A       4S      SendToModule FvwmPiazza Rows 2,66
# Key w               A       4       SendToModule FvwmPiazza Wide 3
# Key w               A       4S      SendToModule FvwmPiazza Wide 3,Bottom
# Key g               A       4       SendToModule FvwmPiazza Grid 4,2
# Key g               A       4S      SendToModule FvwmPiazza Grid 4,2,60,50

# Key less    A       4S      SendToModule FvwmPiazza Decrement 1
# Key greater A       4S      SendToModule FvwmPiazza Increment 1

# Key Left    A       4C      Current (!CirculateHit) SendToModule FvwmPiazza PrevGroup
# Key k       A       4S      Current (!CirculateHit) SendToModule FvwmPiazza PrevGroup
# Key Right   A       4C      Current (!CirculateHit) SendToModule FvwmPiazza NextGroup
# Key j       A       4S      Current (!CirculateHit) SendToModule FvwmPiazza NextGroup

# Key Up              A       M4       SendToModule FvwmPiazza Increment 1
# Key Down            A       M4       SendToModule FvwmPiazza Decrement 1

