    NeverFocus, !Handles, FixedPosition, Iconifiable, FixedSize, \
    CirculateSkip, CirculateSkipIcon, Borders, !StickyStippledTitle, \
    !StickyStippledIconTitle, !Closable, IconTitleFormat ButtonBar, \
    TitleFormat ButtonBar, UseStyle NoMax

